Why Join CuEngine?

To benefit from the most innovative approach to make real estate sales easier, quicker, and more efficient.

What makes CuEngine the leading international real estate sales company in Turkey?

Since its establishment in 2019, CuEngine has revolutionized the way real estate sales are made. With over (ex:200 million dollars) generated in revenue from the projects that CuEngine has been managing, within such short time frame.

Sales Service

Promotion :

  • Promotion of projects with events and exhibitions
  • International events (Cityscape, MIPIM, etc)
  • Local events
  • Presentations

Marketing:

  • Marketing on social media platforms such as Instagram, YouTube, Facebook, LinkedIn and Twitter
  • Providing marketing support to agents

Networking:

  • Access to CuEngine International Agents Network
  • Over 2000 agents from 20+ countries

Back Office Support:

  • Agent training on how to sell properties remotely via CuEngine
  • Multilingual team to raise brand awareness
  • Online reservation support for international off-site sales

After Sales Services

  • VAT Exemption procedure
  • International money transfer strategy
  • Assistance with citizenship procedure
  • Title deed and payment follow-up

Partnership Benefits

  • Cutting-edge presentation technology
  • The best commission and price offers
  • Professional marketing support
  • Professional language support in Turkish, English, Arabic, Persian, Russian and Chinese
  • Legal support for title-deed and citizenship
  • Financial consultation
  • Office space for meetings and appointments
  • Special offers and rates
  • Special promotions

Agency Relations Support

  • Establishing relations with agents
  • Contracts with agents
  • Enrollment and training for CuEngine
  • Creating the marketing materials for the project
  • Settlement of payments
  • Assisting international agents through legal procedures and citizenship
